joscelyn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2016/06/al-qaeda-and-allies-gain-more-ground-in-aleppo-province.php|title=Al Qaeda and allies gain more ground in Aleppo province - FDD's Long War Journal|work=longwarjournal.org}}</ref><ref>http://www.peypi.com/detay/rejim-cetelerinin-kacarken-arakalarinda-biraktigi-ganimetlerin-bir-kismi-lazkiye-kinessibba/868278{{dead link|date=October 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> the [[Siege of Al-Fu'ah-Kafarya (2015)]],<ref>{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E0rUHZ8yXno|title=\u0424\u0443\u0430 \u043c\u0438\u043d\u0442\u0430\u049b\u0430\u0441\u0438 \u0436\u0430\u043d\u0433\u043b\u0430\u0440\u0438 - Fua mintaqasi janglari|date=19 September 2015|work=YouTube|accessdate=25 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/syriancivilwar/comments/3lknsk/katiba_turkistani_fighting_in_the_fuah_offensive/|title=Katiba Turkistani[?] fighting in the Fu'ah offensive : syriancivilwar|work=reddit|accessdate=25 October 2015}}</ref> and the seizure of the Qarmid military camp.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://videoonline.su/video/6URQiQOQWXI|title=\u049a\u0430\u0440\u043c\u0438\u0434 \u043c\u0443\u0430\u0441\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0438 \u0443\u0447\u0443\u043d \u0436\u0430\u043d\u0433\u043b\u0430\u0440|accessdate=25 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928053701/http://videoonline.su/video/6URQiQOQWXI|archive-date=28 September 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nw0mGam0n5w&t=3m8s|title=\u049a\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0438\u0434 \"\u041a\u0443\u0444\u0440\" \u043c\u0443\u0430\u0441\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0433\u0430 \u04b3\u0443\u0436\u0443\u043c - Qormid \"Kufr\" muaskariga hujum|date=30 April 2015|work=YouTube|accessdate=25 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://videoonline.su/video/Nw0mGam0n5w|title=\u049a\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0438\u0434 '\u041a\u0443\u0444\u0440' \u043c\u0443\u0430\u0441\u043a\u0